{"tid":368071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"16歲美女就逼4幼女賣淫　PO照供嫖客選擇 遭判13年","createTime":"2017-08-21T09:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T09:53:50.000Z","uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67c93eabbd88552dc695ebdf9520fffa812ebf95","tid":368071,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T09:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.ettoday.net/images/2640/d2640522.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2640%2Fd2640522.jpg&h=e0988a0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲美18歲少女仲介4名未成年少女進行性交易，遭判刑13年。（圖／翻攝Fresno Bee）<br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n美國加州18歲的艾爾瑪利歐（Jelinajane Bedrijo Almario）透過網路和朋友結識未成年少女後，再將她們推入火坑賣淫。法院表示，少女犯案時年僅16歲，竟強迫4名14到15歲的少女賣淫，，3日依人口販賣和拉皮條等罪，判刑13年。<br />\n<br />\n金斯郡警探彭特科沃（Richard Pontecorvo）表示，住在金斯郡（Kings County）漢福德（Hanford）的艾爾瑪利歐是賣淫集團的首腦，16歲的她透過朋友介紹和網路交友，認識了4名被害少女。<br />\n<br />\n彭特科沃指出，艾爾瑪利歐會故意去和這些少女做朋友，誘騙她們離家出走後，翻臉叫少女們賣淫，並將這些受害者的照片拍照PO網，供顧客選用。<br />\n<br />\n彭特科沃也說，這些少女本來就屬於比較自卑的人，所以容易受到操控，艾爾瑪利歐會載著她們到鄰近的圖萊里郡（Tulare County）的99號公路旁的汽車旅館進行性交易，「這些皮條客已經在少女們的心中造成陰影，但還好我們非常早就逮捕犯人，讓少女們逃離火海。」法院3日依人口販賣和拉皮條，判艾爾瑪利歐13年徒刑。"},{"pid":"e33a118df94e1acac1e95362e95c94990059988a","tid":368071,"uid":29011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T09:26:00.000Z","msg":"美女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179487bfe44edf91bd4005fef1052b73c729fbd6","tid":368071,"uid":4243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T09:26:03.000Z","msg":"肥婆真係無個好人"},{"pid":"9415427b1ff7ca7446c7789f304a291d65b544f6","tid":368071,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T09:26:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"184afac589f5f1d840a4e4a70ca0644b2c7d2e24","tid":368071,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T09:26:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肥婆真係無個好人</blockquote><br />\n冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4d68784512791e509de0bf0ddbaa83e8532b54","tid":368071,"uid":125079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T09:31:59.000Z","msg":"美女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中國既係咪叫中女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba57f8a24349dd8b7914e3b2a3984273c60a20c0","tid":368071,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T09:33:12.000Z","msg":"美國女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6c33da4ea38d6f6db4c7642b28c44ccd2bad21","tid":368071,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T09:52:57.000Z","msg":"差緊啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d43f3abd2c4ddabf7e0b93453beb18255ce0a6a","tid":368071,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T09:53:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}